<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Reservations</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Restaurant Reservations</h1>
  <p>Use the API endpoints to manage reservations.</p>
  <ul>
    <li>GET /reservation — list all reservations</li>
    <li>GET /reservation/:id — get a reservation</li>
    <li>POST /reservation — create a reservation (requires auth)</li>
    <li>PUT /reservation/:id — update a reservation (requires auth)</li>
    <li>DELETE /reservation/:id — cancel a reservation (requires auth)</li>
  </ul>
</body>
</html>
